### 1. Install TFTP
```
#apt update; sudo apt install tftp-hpa tftpd-hpa
```

### 2. Edit the TFTP config file...
```
#vim /etc/default/tftpd-hpa
```
 
with this configuration
```
RUN_DAEMON="yes"
TFTP_USERNAME="tftp"
TFTP_DIRECTORY="/var/lib/tftpboot"
TFTP_ADDRESS=":69"
TFTP_OPTIONS="--secure --create"
```
 
### 3. Configure the permissions for the TFTP root folder
```
#chmod 755 /var/lib/tftpboot
#chown tftp:tftp /var/lib/tftpboot
```
 
### 4. Restart the TFTP service
```
#service tftpd-hpa restart
```